	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>What's happening with new MMC5 boards and flash devices?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was curious about the how far along the development of MMC5 with new flash carts and boards. To my knowledge, none of the existing devices available are able to replicate the MMC5 yet. I have a translation in progress of a 1MB PRG-ROM, 512kb CHR-ROM MMC5 game and to my knowledge it's not playable on hardware with existing hardware/devices. Using an existing board as a donor does not appear it would work, and I am perfectly content with that. <br /><br />So I was just wondering if MMC5 support was coming soon or not.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


