	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Are you using the MMC5 for it's  1MB prg-rom capabilities alone?  Or are you looking for all the extra capabilities as well?<br /><br />My boards can support up to 1MB of parallel rom.  We've had a few discussions recently about different means of mapper support (stripped down MMC5, expanded MMC3, etc).<br /><!-- l --><a class="postlink-local" href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=9&amp;t=10508">viewtopic.php?f=9&amp;t=10508</a><!-- l --><br /><!-- l --><a class="postlink-local" href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=10&amp;t=10474">viewtopic.php?f=10&amp;t=10474</a><!-- l -->

		

		</td>
