		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: What's happening with new MMC5 boards and flash devices?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />My Z-machine interpreter (versions 1, 2, 3 only) requires 64K PRG RAM (the only reason it uses MMC5) and 32+32F PRG ROM bankswitching; I deliberately avoid use of all other features, so that a cartridge can more easily be made if anyone wants to do so. (It also uses the keyboard, but that isn't a part of the mapper.)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


